Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会被你祝贺啊
