Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是A-LAWS的精英  很可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么会知道？
