Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向沙慈开枪这种事…
